node.text: The search for epic demands good crew with true send-and-see commitment, and this 8-day adventure with @kennysmith9 and friends delivered. Brotherhood, blind faith, and bears - limits were pushed, but all for the sake of time on 2 wheels and endless trails. Link in bio for the full length edit 👆 #sendthesearch 🎥 @ambrose_weingart
